      <guid>http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/221025_tibor-kalman_consistency-not-sameness/</guid>
      <description><![CDATA[<p>Important characteristic of a great brand is consistency. This is different from sameness. Sameness is static &amp; lifeless. Consistency is responsive and vibrant.</p>
