    <item>
      <title></title>
      <link>http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/220523_vangelis_invest-in-beauty/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 May 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/220523_vangelis_invest-in-beauty/</guid>
      <description><![CDATA[<p>What we need today more than anything else is to invest in beauty, because beauty is harmony which comes from chaos. But we invest in chaos, because chaos is much more profitable than peace&hellip; Beauty is a kind of safety vault for people.</p>
]]></description>
      
    </item>
    
    
    
    <item>
      <title></title>
      <link>http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/211107_mike-watt_punk-is-a-state/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Nov 2021 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/211107_mike-watt_punk-is-a-state/</guid>
      <description><![CDATA[<p>Maybe you gotta understand what punk meant to us. With the Minutemen, punk was not a style of music. It was the state of your mind. We thought the style of music was up to each band. For us punk meant if you find yourself not fitting in a certain kind of world, you try to create your own.</p>
]]></description>
      
    </item>
    
    
    
